OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777551071
OL,3,COne of UK's rarest mammals handed in
OL,4,Cto Tewkesbury wildlife rescue centre
OL,6,FOne of the UK's rarest native mammals
OL,7,Fhas been handed in to Vale Wildlife
OL,8,FHospital & Rehabilitation Centre in
OL,9,FTewkesbury.
OL,11,FOn the evening of 21 April, the
OL,12,Fwildlife rescue centre had a pine
OL,13,Fmarten, weighing only 105g, brought
OL,14,Finto their hospital.
OL,16,FThe tiny kit was discovered in a
OL,17,Frubbish bin alongside two deceased
OL,18,Fsiblings. The pine marten was then
OL,19,Fbrought into the centre by a hedgehog
OL,20,Fcarer who believed he might be a fox
OL,21,Fcub.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
