PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777551071
OL,3,COne of UK's rarest mammals handed in
OL,4,Cto Tewkesbury wildlife rescue centre
OL,6,FNatalie Gould, who works at Vale
OL,7,FWildlife Hospital & Rehabilitation
OL,8,FCentre described how special it is for
OL,9,Fthe animal to have been brought into
OL,10,Ftheir care, explaining how in the 42
OL,11,Fyears for which the centre has been
OL,12,Fopen they have never had a pine marten
OL,13,Fadmitted.
OL,15,FShe went on to say how the little
OL,16,Fanimal is "absolutely adorable" but is
OL,17,F"very loud".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
