OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777551071
OL,3,COne of UK's rarest mammals handed in
OL,4,Cto Tewkesbury wildlife rescue centre
OL,6,F"His eyes and ears are still closed at
OL,7,Fthe moment, he is blind and deaf, up
OL,8,Funtil about 5 weeks of age. We guess
OL,9,Fhe is around the 2 weeks mark at the
OL,10,Fmoment, but sadly we don't know for
OL,11,Fcertain."
OL,13,FThe centre explained how the little
OL,14,Fkit is now in the care of one of their
OL,15,Fexperienced hand-rearing team members
OL,16,Fand will stay with them until he's
OL,17,Fweaned. They will then gradually
OL,18,Fbecome more hands-off to ensure he
OL,19,Fdoesn't become imprinted - which will
OL,20,Fgive him the best possible chance at
OL,21,Flife back in the wild.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
