PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777551071
OL,3,COne of UK's rarest mammals handed in
OL,4,Cto Tewkesbury wildlife rescue centre
OL,6,FPine martens were once widespread
OL,7,Facross the UK however they suffered
OL,8,Fhuge declines due to habitat loss and
OL,9,Fhistoric persecution, due to their
OL,10,Fthick fur. The wildlife centre says
OL,11,Fadmissions like this show signs that
OL,12,Fthe populations are slowly recovering.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
